{"title":"深秋的滋味","authors":["孙昕晨"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深秋的滋味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙昕晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水的凉意是音乐的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从我的脚趾爬上来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷暴雨浓缩成一颗葡萄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静地躺在掌心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是秋天了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个奶水丰沛的季节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空因为土地的沉重而高远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的感情也染成紫扁豆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会飞翔或者伫立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是多么了不起的事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同大雁或者向日葵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天，正是用这种姿势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我们交谈着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它使我们懂得——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如何吮吸天空和大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白露、寒露、霜降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一件一件加衣裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在黄昏的天井里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看季节的趾爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北屋爬上南墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月渐渐冷了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜渐渐白了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是迁移还是固守？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和一棵树争论不休的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花的手掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经悄悄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搭在了我们的肩上！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}